      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, collector-grade vehicle that stands as a testament to meticulous ownership. The exterior is finished in a deep, mirror-like metallic paint that has been protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating; there are absolutely no rock chips, swirl marks, or door dings to be found. Every body line is laser-straight, and the original alloy wheels are pristine, devoid of any curb rash. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom condition, featuring premium leather upholstery that shows zero bolster wear and retains its original matte finish. All technological features, from the high-fidelity sound system to the intuitive touchscreen interface, function exactly as they did the day it rolled off the assembly line. Mechanically, this car is peerless. It has been strictly garage-kept in a climate-controlled environment and has never seen rain or snow. A complete, chronological service history from authorized specialists accompanies the sale, confirming that every maintenance milestone was met early. This is a rare find for a buyer who demands perfection and a vehicle that looks, smells, and drives like new.",
